          "html_excerpt": "Arduino Projects for Dummies In 2013, I wrote\u00a0Arduino Projects for Dummies\u00a0in the popular how-to series by publisher John Wiley & Sons. The book describes a dozen interactive projects based on the popular Arduino microcontroller prototyping platform. It has\u00a0simple, clear explanations, step-by-step\u00a0instructions and plenty of images and illustrations. You can get a copy of my book on the ForDummies website, at Amazon, or at your local bookstore."
